    "Encoder-decoder LLMs (e.g., ChatGLM [7]) are useful for tasks that involve both understanding and generating text, such as summarization.",
    "Decoder-only LLMs (e.g., GPT-4 [8]) excel at generative tasks such as sentence completion and open-ended generation.",
